<!--자동차_정보-->
{{TemplateMapping
| mapToClass = Automobile
| mappings =
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =이름 | ontologyProperty =foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 제조사 | ontologyProperty = manufacturer }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 모회사 | ontologyProperty =parentCompany }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =별명 | ontologyProperty =foaf:nick }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =생산년도 | ontologyProperty =productionStartYear }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =출시년도 | ontologyProperty =modelStartYear }}
	{{DateIntervalMapping | templateProperty = 판매기간 | startDateOntologyProperty = modelStartDate | endDateOntologyProperty = modelEndDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =조립 | ontologyProperty =assembly }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =선행차량 | ontologyProperty =predecessor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =후속차량 | ontologyProperty = successor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =차체형식 | ontologyProperty = bodyStyle }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =차종 | ontologyProperty =class }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty =엔진 | ontologyProperty =engine }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 최고출력 | ontologyProperty = powerOutput | unit = Power }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 전장 | ontologyProperty = length | unit = Length }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 전폭 | ontologyProperty = width | unit = Length }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 전고 | ontologyProperty = height | unit = Length }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 전비중량 | ontologyProperty = weight | unit = Mass }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 연료적재량 | ontologyProperty = fuelCapacity | unit = Volume }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 설계자 | ontologyProperty = designer }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 설계자 | ontologyProperty = designCompany }}


end}}
